:

*Stigla je pre nego što smo očekivali. (It arrived earlier than we expected.)

*Došao je što pre da bi stigao na vreme. (He came as soon as he could to make it in time.)

*Stigli smo na vreme za početak događaja. (We arrived on time for the start of the event.)

*Stiže nam pomoć. (Help is coming.)

*Stizali su studenti iz svih krajeva sveta. (Students were coming from all over the world.)